  "texts": [
    "Covariance values were examined to facilitate the refinement process, and variables within the same factor with the highest values were associated.",
    "As seen in Fig. 1, modification indices were also examined, and associations were established between variables with the highest Modification Index (M.I.)",
    "scores (e9 < -> e10 and e13 < -> e14).",
    "In CFA, the factor loading of items is examined considering the standard regression coefficients.",
    "Additionally, the adequacy of factor loadings and the significance of standard regression coefficients are assessed to make decisions (Kartal & Bardakçı, 2018)."
  ]
}